title: 147.012 OVERSIGHT OF ALLIED HEALTH PROFESSIONS.
text: The board has responsibility for the oversight of the following allied health professions: physician assistants under chapter 147A, acupuncture practitioners under chapter 147B, respiratory care practitioners under chapter 147C, traditional midwives under chapter 147D, registered naturopathic doctors under chapter 147E, genetic counselors under chapter 147F, and athletic trainers under sections 148.7801 to 148.7815.
